  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your Twisted Chakra forms wings, gills, or claws that allow you the ability of special movement such as flight, swimming, or burrowing.</p><p>You gain the following benefits only when you are gaining the benefits of Twisted Chakra Cloak:</p><p>• You gain a flying, burrow, or swimming speed equal to your speed. (Choose one)<br />• When you would trigger an attack of opportunity while flying, swimming, or burrowing, the triggering attack is made at disadvantage.<br />• You can, as a reaction, use your wings or chakra arms to intercept an attack that would deal damage to you. Your wings have 40 hit points. When their hit points are reduced to 0, they are destroyed until you use a Full Turn Action and 15 Twisted Chakra to regenerate them.</p>",
